<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>Hatak o̱ haknip okʋt, Illit falamʋt tani.</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hatak o̱ haknip okʋto,
 Yakni yak o̱ atoba hosh,
 Yakosi itintakla ho̱,
 Okcha̱yat ahanta hoke.

[V2]
 Atuk osh chekosi fehna,
 Pi̱ Chitokaka holba hosh,
 Im aholluppi yatuk ma,
 Kahʋlma̱yat nusi hoke.

[V3]
 Yohmi tok ik nana kia,
 Illit falamʋt tani tok
 Okchalinchi Chisʋs okʋt
 Falʋmmi̱t tanicha chishke.

[V4]
 Yohmi hoka an Chisʋs a̱,
 Immi toba li tuk ocha,
 Yʋmmʋt ʋba ya̱ mintikma,
 Afama ka̱ sa bʋnnashke.

[V5]
 Mikmʋt sʋlli tok oh kia,
 Chisʋs okʋt immaiyachi,
 Hatok oka, nan illi ha̱,
 Immaiyachi la chi̱ hoke.</lyrics>
<title>Resurection ƲIT168</title>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<hymn_number>168</hymn_number>
</song>